Description: This Archive contains the publications produced by the Understanding Children's Work (UCW) Project.
As part of broader efforts to develop effective and long-term solutions to child labour, ILO, UNICEF and the World Bank launched the joint interagency research project in December 2000. All UCW Working papers and UCW Country studies are immediately available in pdf. For more information please consult our website www.ucw-project.org.
